text: Bâgé-Dommartin is a new commune in the Ain department in the Auvergne-Rhône- Alpes region of east France. It started on January 1, 2018 and has the former communes of Bâgé-la-Ville and Dommartin in it.Arrêté préfectoral 8 December 2017 == References == Category:2018 establishments in France Category:Communes in Ain
title: Bâgé-Dommartin
